{"tid":2187113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（大爆發！）內地到澳門明起持7日有效核酸陰性證明填健康碼可入境","createTime":"2020-09-03T12:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T12:26:18.000Z","uid":66087,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5084397649f1c765cad7b51cfdecece86c86bd39","tid":2187113,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547701-20200903.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547701-20200903.htm&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=e7de05c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547701-20200903.htm&h=507268b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547701-20200903.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-09-03 HKT 18:53<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門逐步推進恢復與內地的人員往來，由明日開始，所有從內地入境澳門的人士，均毋須接受14天醫學隔離，包括新疆烏魯木齊，亦由零時起，取消入境後的隔離措施，全部只需提交7日有效的新冠病毒核酸陰性證明，以及填報健康碼，便可入境。"},{"pid":"ce92b5cc8ba0867c5aaf3b4d0af107cbde6b1345","tid":2187113,"uid":343754,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0dcde01db979defa747e8a680d83f4d37feabf","tid":2187113,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"呢2個星期密切留意澳門疫情情況，就可以知道支那疫情真相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdff26c153bf141689a256117b4c739de553f0b","tid":2187113,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eed5b8eff7592c1b8cddc2400f39161d7b8769e8","tid":2187113,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1